data.name: ReadCashReceiptCashReceiptDetail
data.value: select top(1) T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER, T1.CST_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER, T1.RECEIPT_AMOUNT, T1.CASH_RECEIPT_ID, T1.RECEIPT_DATE, T1.CHECK_TYPE, T1.CHECK_NUMBER, T1.CHECK_DATE, T1.RECEIVED_DATE, T1.DEPOSIT_RLSE_DT, T1.REFERENCE_NUMBER, T1.PAYOR_ORGANIZATION, T1.PAYOR_FIRST_NAME, T1.PAYOR_MIDDLE_NAME, T1.PAYOR_LAST_NAME, T1.FRWRD_TO_NAME, T1.FRWRD_STREET_1, T1.FRWRD_STREET_2, T1.FRWRD_CITY, T1.FRWRD_STATE, T1.FRWRD_ZIP5, T1.FRWRD_ZIP4, T1.FRWRD_ZIP3, T1.BAL_TMST, T1.TOTAL_CASH_TRANSAC, T1.TOT_NONCSH_TRN_AMT, T1.TOT_CASH_TRAN_CNT, T1.TOT_NOCSH_TRAN_CNT, T1.TOT_DETAIL_ADJ_CNT, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CASH_BAL_AMT, T1.CASH_BAL_RSN, T1.CASH_DUE, T1.TOTAL_NC_FEE_AMT, T1.TOT_CASH_FEE_AMT, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T1.NOTE, T1.PAYOR_SSN, T2.CRD_ID, T2.INTERFACE_TRAN_ID, T2.ADJUSTMENT_IND, T2.COURT_ORDER_NUMBER, T2.CASE_NUMBER, T2.OFFSET_TAXID, T2.RECEIVED_AMOUNT, T2.COLLECTION_AMOUNT, T2.COLLECTION_DATE, T2.MULTI_PAYOR, T2.OFFSET_TAX_YEAR, T2.JOINT_RETURN_IND, T2.JOINT_RETURN_NAME, T2.DFLTD_COLL_DAT_IND, T2.OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR, T2.OBLGOR_SSN, T2.OBLGOR_FIRST_NM, T2.OBLGOR_LAST_NM, T2.OBLGOR_MID_NM, T2.OBLGOR_PHONE_NBR, T2.PAYEE_FIRST_NAME, T2.PAYEE_MIDDLE_NAME, T2.PAYEE_LAST_NAME, T2.SUP_PRSN_FRST_NM1, T2.SUP_PRSN_MID_NM1, T2.SUP_PRSN_LST_NM1, T2.SUP_PRSN_FRST_NM2, T2.SUP_PRSN_LST_NM2, T2.SUP_PRSN_MID_NM2, T2.CREATED_BY, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T2.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T2.REFUNDED_AMT, T2.DISTRIBUTED_AMT, T2.COLLAMT_APPL_IND, T2.SUPP_PERS_NO_VOL, T2.REFERENC, T2.NOTES, T2.OVRRD_MNL_DIST_IND from CKT_CASH_RECEIPT T1 join CKT_CR_DETAIL T2 on (T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CST_IDENTIFIER = T2.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CRD_ID = @crdId) and (T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER = @crvIdentifier) and (T2.CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER = @crtIdentifier)

data.name: ReadCollection
data.value: select top(1) T1.COLL_ID, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.OTY_ID, T1.OB_TRN_AMT from CKT_OB_TRN T2 join CKT_COLLECTION T1 on (T1.COLL_ID = @collId) and (T2.OTY_TYPE = T1.OTY_ID) and (T2.OB_TRN_TYP = T1.OTR_TYPE) and (T2.OB_TRN_ID = T1.OTR_ID) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T1.OBG_ID) and (T2.CPA_SUP_TYPE = 'S') and (T2.CSP_SUP_NUMBER = @cspSupNumber)

data.name: ReadUraExcessCollection
data.value: select top(1) SEQ_NUMBER, AMOUNT, COLLECTION_ACTION, SUPPLYING_CSE_PER, INITIATING_COLL, INITIATING_CSE_PER from CKT_URA_XS_COLL where SEQ_NUMBER = @seqNumber
